== git-lh - Lighthouse update script

Original script at http://pastie.org/298043

Added support for syncing remote branches.

== Installation

cp git-lh /usr/local/bin

Add the following to your .git/config:

[lighthouse]
  token = your_lh_api_token
  account = your_lh_account
  project = your_lh_project_id

== Usage

Before pushing to a central repo, run git lh.  All commits not yet pushed will be logged to Lighthouse.
